Class Entity

java.lang.Object
Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlueIceEntity, GreenNatureEntity, RedFireEntity
public abstract class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
The Entity class is a Product Class. This Entity represents the enemies and the player characters. It has 3 types: Blue/Ice, Red/Fire, Green/Nature and 3 styles: Atlantis, Valhalla, Underwild.
